title: SoundPEATS Magnetic Wireless Earbuds Bluetooth Headphones Sport in-Ear Sweatproof Earphones with Mic (Super Sound Quality, IPX6, Bluetooth 4.1, aptx, 8 Hours Play Time, Secure Fit Design) (Black)
